<p>THIRD KIT</p>

<p>And there is the hat-trick. Three strips, all identical except for the colours.</p>

<p>And even that is debateable, with the third kit also based on an early 1990s design, it shares the same yellow colours as the away kit, differing only in having red rather than green.</p>

<p>This alone earns it a deducted point in our verdict, but it does remind us of a past-era of WWE wrestling when Hulk Hogan was top dog. So beware of Baggie-maniacs running wild in this strip next term, brother.</p>

