<p>AWAY KIT</p>

<p>Retro continues to be the inspiration behind the away kit for West Ham's 125th anniversary and there really is nothing they can do wrong when they bring back an old favourite such as this.</p>

<p>The blue kit with two claret hoops across the front has regularly made an appearance since it was made popular in the 1960s by the greats mentioned in the home kit description.</p>

<p>Being picky, the colouring of the sponsor is a little out but Hammers fans won't be turning their nose up at this throwback.</p>

<p>AWAY KIT VERDICT: 8/10¬†</p>

